  "remarks": "Alexander Reznik is the General Director of JSC Petrovsky Electromechanical Plant “Molot”, which is a military industry company producing various components and instruments for weapons used in the war of aggression against Ukraine. JSC Petrovsky Electromechanical Plant “Molot” is a subsidiary of JSC Concern Granit-Electron, which is part of JSC Tactical Missiles Corporation.",
